13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekiston aholisi uchun sovuq suv tariflari (2025-yildan amal qiladi) hisoblagich mavjudligiga bog'liq. Suv hisoblagich bo'lganda haqiqiy iste'mol bo'yicha, bo'lmaganda — har bir kishiga normativ bo'yicha to'lanadi. Sovuq suvning o'rtacha tarifi 3 000-5 000 so'm/m³, oqava suv (kanalizatsiya) — qo'shimcha 1 500-3 000 so'm/m³."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblagichsiz iste'mol normativlari: bir kishiga kuniga 150-200 litr (oyiga 4,5-6 m³). 4 kishilik oila hisoblagichsiz: 4 × 6 = 24 m³/oy × 4 000 so'm = 96 000 so'm suv uchun + oqava suv ≈ 48 000 so'm, jami 144 000 so'm. Hisoblagich bilan: odatda 8-15 m³/oy: 12 × 4 000 = 48 000 + 24 000 = 72 000 so'm. Tejash: hisoblagich o'rnatishda 50% gacha."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Issiq suv ta'minoti — alohida xarajat moddasi. Markaziy issiq suv ta'minotli uylarda tarif sovuq suv va isitish narxini o'z ichiga oladi. Gaz suv isitgichli (kolonkali) uylarda issiq suv narxi sovuq suv sarfi va isitish uchun gaz sarfidan tashkil topadi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Suv hisoblagichni o'rnatish yangi uy-joy uchun majburiy va mavjud uy-joy uchun tavsiya etiladi. O'rnatish narxi: 200 000-500 000 so'm. Tekshirish har 4-6 yilda o'tkaziladi. Ko'rsatkichlar har oy mobil ilova yoki suv kanali abonent bo'limi orqali uzatiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"To'liq kommunal xarajatlarni (suv + elektr + gaz + isitish) hisoblash uchun kommunal xizmatlar kalkulyatorimizdan foydalaning. Suvni tejash tavsiyalari: kranlarga aeratorlar o'rnating (30-50% tejash); kir va idish yuvish mashinasini to'liq yuklab ishlating; oqayotgan kranlarni ta'mirlang."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":[["$","caption",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 text-left font-medium text-foreground bg-muted/50 border-b border-border","children":"Elektr energiya tariflari (so'm/kVt·s)"}],["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"className":"bg-muted/30","children":[["$","th","0",{"className":"px-4 py-2.5 text-left font-medium text-foreground border-b border-border","children":"Iste'mol hajmi"}],["$","th","1",{"className":"px-4 py-2.5 text-left font-medium text-foreground border-b border-border","children":"1 kVt·s narxi"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":["$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d"]}]]}]}],"$L1e","$L1f"]]}],"$L20","$L21"]}]
